OL,3,CFather of Sara Sharif denies being
OL,4,C'manipulative and controlling man'
OL,6,FSara Sharif's father has denied being
OL,7,Fa "lying", "manipulative" and
OL,8,F"controlling" man, as he stands trial
OL,9,Ffor murdering his 10-year-old daughter.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the Old Bailey on Monday,
OL,12,FTaxi driver Urfan Sharif, 42, denied
OL,13,Fkilling his 10-year-old daughter by
OL,14,Fbeating her.
OL,16,FSharif said he returned from work to
OL,17,Ffind Sara "collapsed" after his wife,
OL,18,FBeinash Batool, called him home on the
OL,19,Fevening of August 8 last year.
