OL,6,FHe was cross-examined in court by
OL,7,FBatool's barrister, having previously
OL,8,Faccused his wife of abusing Sara, who
OL,9,Fis her stepdaughter.
OL,11,FCaroline Carberry KC asked him: "You
OL,12,Fare a lying, manipulative and
OL,13,Fcontrolling man, aren't you?", to
OL,14,Fwhich he responded: "No, I am not."
OL,16,FThe barrister detailed Sharif's
OL,17,Fhistory of alleged domestic violence,
OL,18,Fwhich the defendant denied.
