OL,6,FSharif was also asked if he is a
OL,7,F"cruel father", as he stated in a
OL,8,Fphone call to police from Pakistan in
OL,9,Fthe early hours of August 10, 2023.
OL,11,FSharif responded: "I said I was cruel
OL,12,Fbecause I left my daughter behind, I
OL,13,Fshould not have done that.J"I did not
OL,14,Fkill my daughter by beating her."
OL,16,FSharif was shown photographic and
OL,17,Fvideo evidence of bruises and marks on
OL,18,FSara, but he denied knowing about them.
